data.description: Juan used his HTML, CSS and Javascript skills to build a website for his own company, Holy Kinetics, a fitness and health brand.

Emiliano created the design and functionality for his food resource app, Rooted, incorporating visual design principles, UX research, user flows and wire framing. Emiliano is planning to launch his app in order to avoid food waste and connect people to essential food resources.

Melissa developed a digital design as part of her passion project. She learned various skills such as computer navigation, Google Suite functionality, digital design, data and project management. Melissa will be able to apply her newly-gained skills to her work within the non-profit space and is excited to learn front-end development with EW next.
